OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FAny
OL,6,Flingering rain quickly moving away
OL,7,Fthis evening, with clear spells
OL,8,Ffollowing. A few showers are possible
OL,9,Fovernight, mainly in the north.
OL,10,FTurning chilly where skies remain
OL,11,Fclear with a patchy rural frost.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTuesday:FA dry day for many with sunny
OL,14,Fspells, though the cloud may be thick
OL,15,Fenough to give the odd light shower in
OL,16,Fthe south. Feeling a little fresher
OL,17,Fthan today.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
